Varsity Corporate is a 1,600sqm two level strata office building which was completed in 2005.  The building comprises of 5 strata office suites of which all are owner occupied.

The building is located on the corner of Varsity Parade and Main Parade, Varsity Lakes and sits on adjacent to the Minter Ellison Building.

Varsity Corporate offers its occupants a parking ratio of 1 bay per 30sqm with both basement and podium level parking areas.

* 291sqm strata office suite (approx.)
* 5 basement bays +  6 on-grade bays
* Full corporate fitout - ready to move in
* Available with vacant possession
* Move in over Christmas/New Year

Sale by Expression of Interest closing Wednesday, 10th December 2008.

Tania Moore on 0439 034 025

183 Varsity Parade is a prominent office building providing a premium investment opportunity within the heart of the Varsity Lakes commercial precinct. 

This modern two-level commercial office building was refurbished in 2020, offers a 100kW solar system and holds a 4.5-star NABERS Energy rating. 

Located on the corner of Varsity Parade, the building benefits from substantial traffic flow into Varsity Square and the surrounding retail amenities. Furthermore, the property is located directly across from QLD State Government Varsity College and 500 metres* from Bond University providing outstanding access to educational establishments.

- Modern refurbished two-storey office building 
- Fully leased net income $1,085,702 per annum*

On behalf of the seller, CBRE has the pleasure in offering for sale Suite 107, 'Lakeside 3', 20 Lake Orr Drive, Varsity Lakes (Lot 10 on SP182366).

The subject offering comprises 173sqm* of first floor office space currently unoccupied. 'Lakeside 3' is located just off Bermuda Street, an arterial commercial thoroughfare in Varsity Lakes, bordering Burleigh Waters, surrounded by professional offices and services, cafes and retail. The offering boasts views over Lake Orr and the sublime architecture of Bond University.

The suite has been subject to a recent internal refurbishment, presenting well for immediate occupancy by an incoming owner/tenant.

Suite 107, 20 Lake Orr Drive, Varsity Lakes is being offered For Sale via Offers to Purchase, closing 4:00pm Thursday 10th November 2016.
